g.text: Makes Http Request to get Medical Condition data
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDV
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Displays the fetched data and asks for the new Medical Condition's data
Sends Medical Condition's data (MedicalConditionCode, MedicalConditionName, MedicalConditionDescription, MedicalConditionSymptoms)
Makes Http Request to update an MedicalCondition
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDV
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Validates Medical Condition's data and updates it
